item.title: CVE-2023-5979|2023-12-04T21:27:37.654Z -- unknown -- ecommerce%20product%20catalog%20plugin%20for%20wordpress
item.description: The eCommerce Product Catalog Plugin for WordPress plugin before 3.3.26 does not have CSRF checks in some of its admin pages, which could allow attackers to make logged-in users perform unwanted actions via CSRF attacks, such as delete all products
